OL,3,CMan appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cmurder after fatal house fire
OL,6,FA man has appeared in court accused of
OL,7,Fmurder in connection with a fatal
OL,8,Fhouse fire in Wolverhampton.
OL,10,FDale Francis, 36, attended a hearing
OL,11,Fat Wolverhampton Crown Court on
OL,12,FTuesday via video-link from HMP
OL,13,FBirmingham charged with murder, four
OL,14,Fcounts of attempted murder and one
OL,15,Fcount of arson with intent to endanger
OL,16,Flife.
