OL,3,CMan appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cmurder after fatal house fire
OL,6,FThe charges are in connection with a
OL,7,Ffire at a house in Plascom Road in
OL,8,FEast Park, Wolverhampton, in the early
OL,9,Fhours of June 25, which was caught on
OL,10,FCCTV.
OL,12,FAkashdeep Singh, 26, who the court
OL,13,Fheard was trapped upstairs in the
OL,14,Fhouse with his mother and one of his
OL,15,Fbrothers when the fire started, was
OL,16,Frushed to hospital, where he later
OL,17,Fdied.
