OL,3,CMan appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cmurder after fatal house fire
OL,6,FProsecution counsel Sarah Slater told
OL,7,Fthe court Mr Singh's brother suffered
OL,8,Fa fractured back when he fell out of
OL,9,Fan upstairs window, while their mother
OL,10,Fis still in intensive care in hospital.
OL,12,FTwo others were also injured.
OL,14,FFrancis, of Clarke Street in Stoke-on-
OL,15,FTrent, answered "yes sir" when asked
OL,16,Fby Judge Michael Chambers KC, if he
OL,17,Fcould hear him over the link.
