OL,3,CMan appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cmurder after fatal house fire
OL,6,FJudge Chambers told him: "Your case is
OL,7,Fadjourned until the next hearing on
OL,8,FOctober 11 when you should be produced
OL,9,Fat court.
OL,11,F"At this hearing, you will be asked
OL,12,Fwhether you plead guilty or not guilty
OL,13,Fto the charges you face.
OL,15,F"In the meantime, you should remain in
OL,16,Fcustody."
OL,18,FIn a statement issued through West
OL,19,FMidlands Police after Mr Singh's
OL,20,Fdeath, his relatives described him as
OL,21,Fa "true hero".
