OL,3,CMan appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cmurder after fatal house fire
OL,6,FThey said: "Our family is deeply
OL,7,Fshocked and saddened by the news of
OL,8,FAkashdeep Singh's passing.
OL,10,F"He was a kind, helpful, and deeply
OL,11,Freligious person whose loss brings us
OL,12,Fimmense pain that will remain with us
OL,13,Ffor the rest of our lives.
OL,15,F"A true hero, our precious son, whose
OL,16,Fboundless kindness, infectious
OL,17,Flaughter, and unwavering love filled
OL,18,Four lives with immeasurable joy, his
OL,19,Fmemory will forever be cherished, and
OL,20,Fthe depth of his absence is profoundly
OL,21,Ffelt every single day."
